WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:07.860
Every month, the books have to close. And every month, good people give up their nights to get there.

00:08.060 --> 00:15.190
The close takes 6.4 days — and in fifteen years, that number has barely moved.

00:15.390 --> 00:22.280
Three out of four accountants have had to reopen the books to fix an error found after close.

00:22.480 --> 00:28.740
99% report burnout. 300,000 have walked away.

00:28.940 --> 00:32.330
It isn't the people. It's the work.

00:32.530 --> 00:42.220
So we built engines that absorb the mechanical month: drafting, tying out, citing every figure to its source.

00:42.420 --> 00:53.650
Our public demo close runs in 0.15 seconds — checked, on every single run, by a verifier that never gets tired.

00:53.850 --> 01:01.080
Machines do the work. Your people keep the judgment. Sophon Finance Systems.

